### ============================================================================
### UTIL-API-001 | 가이드북 PDF 변환
### Contract status: 보류 기능의 설계 계약 (Phase 2, 구현 전)
### Endpoint: POST /api/gen/docs/{repo_id}/export/pdf
### 관련 기능 ID: DOCS-UTIL-B-201
### 목적: 저장된 Markdown/HTML 가이드북을 PDF로 렌더링한다.
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = replace-me
@repoId = 3f7cc46e-d954-83ab-9f12-013b0c9d2a1e

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gen/docs/{{repoId}}/export/pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{"locale":"ko-KR","includeTableOfContents":true}

### 202 Accepted
### {"code":202,"message":"accepted","data":{"exportId":"export-uuid","status":"queued","format":"pdf"}}
### 오류: 401 UNAUTHORIZED, 404 DOCS_NOT_FOUND, 409 EXPORT_IN_PROGRESS, 500 PDF_RENDER_FAILED
